# Project Structure

```
theme-root/
├── blocks/                    ← ACF Gutenberg blocks (self-contained)
│   ├── config.php             ← Block registration list (human-readable names)
│   ├── blank/                 ← Template for new blocks (auto-copied)
│   ├── {slug}/
│   │   ├── {slug}.php         ← Block render template
│   │   ├── {slug}.scss        ← Source styles
│   │   ├── {slug}.css         ← Compiled CSS (enqueued per-page)
│   │   ├── {slug}.js          ← Block-specific JavaScript
│   │   ├── {slug}.json        ← ACF field group definition
│   │   └── preview.png        ← Editor preview image
│   └── ... (35+ blocks)
│
├── src/
│   ├── sass/
│   │   ├── style.scss         ← Main entry → style.css
│   │   └── partials/
│   │       ├── _abstracts.scss          ← @forward config + mixins
│   │       ├── _abstracts-blocks.scss   ← @forward all (blocks import this)
│   │       ├── _base-selectors.scss / _base-styles.scss
│   │       ├── _font-face.scss / _reboot.scss / _reset.scss
│   │       ├── aos/             ← AOS animation SCSS
│   │       ├── components/      ← header, footer, nav, search
│   │       ├── config/          ← variables, colors, typography, breakpoints
│   │       ├── helpers/         ← buttons, section-spacing, misc, wp
│   │       ├── js-plugins/      ← swiper, lenis, magnific-popup
│   │       ├── mixins/          ← rem, fluid, containers, animations, buttons
│   │       ├── template-parts/  ← swiper-nav, social-links, breadcrumbs
│   │       ├── templates/       ← index, single, multiple-slider
│   │       └── utilities/       ← images, rtl
│   └── js/
│       ├── swiper-init.js       ← esbuild → assets/js/swiper-bundle.js
│       ├── plugins/             ← concat → assets/js/plugins.js
│       └── custom/              ← concat → assets/js/custom.js
│
├── assets/fonts/ images/ js/  ← Compiled output
│
├── functions/                 ← All PHP function files (required by functions.php)
│   ├── helpers.php            ← General helpers (skel_*)
│   ├── hooks.php              ← Theme setup, filters, actions
│   ├── svg-helpers.php        ← SVG sprite/inline
│   ├── acf-block-helpers.php  ← Block rendering helpers
│   ├── register-acf-blocks.php ← ACF block registration
│   ├── enqueue-scripts.php    ← Script/style enqueueing
│   ├── define-constants.php   ← ACF-sourced PHP constants
│   ├── add-image-sizes.php    ← Custom sizes: w480, w768, w1400, w1920
│   └── ... (30+ files)
│
├── template-parts/            ← Reusable PHP partials (get_template_part)
├── templates/                 ← Page templates
├── header.php / footer.php
├── functions.php              ← Requires all functions/*.php
├── style.css                  ← Compiled main stylesheet
├── gulpfile.mjs               ← Build system (Gulp 5)
└── package.json
```

## Key Relationships

- `functions.php` requires every file in `functions/` directory
- `blocks/config.php` lists all blocks → auto-generates files from `blocks/blank/`
- `register-acf-blocks.php` scans `blocks/*/` for `.json` → registers with ACF
- `enqueue-scripts.php` conditionally loads block CSS/JS via `has_block()`
- Block SCSS imports `../../src/sass/partials/abstracts-blocks` for variables/mixins
